column2: SELECT TOP #  s.veldisp, s.veldisperr,s.subclass,s.z  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, p.deVAB_g,  m.mstellar_median, m.mstellar_err,  line.h_alpha_flux, line.h_alpha_flux_err,  line.h_beta_flux, line.h_beta_flux_err,  line.oiii_#_flux, line.oiii_#_flux_err,  line.nii_#_flux, line.nii_#_flux_err,  line.nii_#_flux, line.nii_#_flux_err,  p.petroR5#_g, p.petroR5#err_g, p.petroR9#_g, p.petroR9#err_g FROM PhotoObjall AS p  JOIN specobjall AS s on s.bestobjID = p.objid  JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscBC0# AS m ON m.specobjid = s.specobjid  JOIN galSpecExtra AS bpt on bpt.specObjID = s.specobjid  JOIN galSpecLine As line on line.specObjID = s.specobjid WHERE  s.class = &&& and s.veldisperr > # and s.veldisp > #*s.veldisperr and  p.petroR5#err_u > # and p.petroR5#_u > #*p.petroR5#err_u and  p.petroR5#err_g > # and p.petroR5#_g > #*p.petroR5#err_g and  p.petroR5#err_r > # and p.petroR5#_r > #*p.petroR5#err_r and  p.petroR5#err_i > # and p.petroR5#_i > #*p.petroR5#err_i and  p.petroR5#err_z > # and p.petroR5#_z > #*p.petroR5#err_z and  p.petroR9#err_u > # and p.petroR9#_u > #*p.petroR9#err_u and  p.petroR9#err_g > # and p.petroR9#_g > #*p.petroR9#err_g and  p.petroR9#err_r > # and p.petroR9#_r > #*p.petroR9#err_r and  p.petroR9#err_i > # and p.petroR9#_i > #*p.petroR9#err_i and  p.petroR9#err_z > # and p.petroR9#_z > #*p.petroR9#err_z and  p.petroR5#_u/P.petroR9#_u < # and  p.petroR5#_g/P.petroR9#_g < # and  p.petroR5#_r/P.petroR9#_r < # and  p.petroR5#_i/P.petroR9#_i < # and  p.petroR5#_z/P.petroR9#_z < # and p.deVAB_u># and p.devab_g>#  and p.devab_r > # and p.devab_i > # and p.devab_z>#  and bpt.bptclass = # and  line.h_alpha_flux_err > # and line.h_alpha_flux > #*line.h_alpha_flux_err  and line.h_beta_flux_err > # and line.h_beta_flux > #*line.h_beta_flux_err
